d(RelNode).\n   *\n   * <p>The behavior is undefined if the class hierarchy for dispatching is not\n   * a tree.\n   */\n  List<MetadataHandler<?>> handlers(Class<? extends MetadataHandler<?>> handlerClass);\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777434143120}}
